patthana15.29:1.1_0: Arūpiṁ kusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naarūpī nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.29:2.1_0: Arūpiṁ akusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naarūpī naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana15.29:3.1_0: Rūpiṁ abyākataṁ dhammaṁ paccayā narūpī naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
